{"id": "1293517915575816273", "channel_id": "1293517915575816273", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节  界域伊始\n\n祂从天中来，祂从地中来，祂从海中来，祂从书中来。\n\n赐下四礼，名之界域，予之天赋，化之四方。\n\n其一为生，生生而不息，气动而不止，是为混沌。\n\n其一为灭，狂战亦伤己，性烈而戮王，是为血肉。\n\n其一为变，借物以强身，三变以御敌，是为深海。\n\n其一为受，五逝而轮转，求一世之机，是为超维。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T10:18:23.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293517915575816273", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第六卷·界域书（自编）", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969"}
{"id": "1293606652607594538", "channel_id": "1293517915575816273", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第二节 混沌旧约\n\n天光无明，混沌无约，诸神四散而不滞焉。\n\n遂取亘古之河铸之，得一物，其身细长，其色似银，其形怪异，带齿，谓之钥。\n\n是时，钥至而门扉开，门开而混沌生。\n\n取于过往之愿，生于此世之约。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T16:11:00.031000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293517915575816273", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第六卷·界域书（自编）", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969"}
{"id": "1293603285919465472", "channel_id": "1293603285919465472", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节  生而不存\n\n自远古来，其界荒渺，旧神已去，却无新主。\n\n融蚀漫漫，没入虚空，万畜不宁，无光无暗。\n\n难存之黯，难鸣之哀，难衷之诉，难承之苦。\n\n当是时，四海无波如死域，天矮地裂如灭境，生而难存，孚如死矣。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T15:57:37.350000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293603285919465472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第三卷·苦难纪", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1283686991728218245"]}
{"id": "1293604723248857249", "channel_id": "1293604723248857249", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节 暗若微芒\n\n幻灭三千，一朝闻声，祂自水中来，如琼浆，如玉液。\n\n天星暗淡，地脉翻滚，人间无亮，何日安宁。\n\n有二侍，一拥白石，谓之粟；一执长龙，谓之鱼。\n\n祂于其中，自诩为光，暗若微芒。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T16:03:20.036000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293604723248857249", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第五卷·争斗书", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1283686991728218245"]}
